videoSnippet.title: Nepo's Brilliancy Almost Wins the Olympiad  | Nepo vs Bacrot | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Ian Nepomniachtchi vs Etienne Bacrot
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 11, Oct-05 
Reti Opening (D39)

. Nf3 d5 2. e3 Nf6 3. c4 e6 4. Nc3 Be7 5. b3 O-O 6. Bb2 c5 7. cxd5 Nxd5 8. h4 b6 9. Qb1 h6 10. g4 Bb7 11. Rh3 Nd7 12. g5 h5 13. Bd3 Nb4 14. Bh7+ Kh8 15. Be4 Nd5 16. Ne2 f5 17. gxf6 N7xf6 18. Ng5 Nxe4 19. Qxe4 Bxg5 20. hxg5 Nf4 21. Qxb7 Nd3+ 22. Kf1 Nxb2 23. Rxh5+ Kg8 24. g6
